KAsteroids
----------

You know this game.  It is based on Warwick Allison's QwSpriteField
widget.



Keys
----

Keys are hard coded currently.

Rotate Left       Left Arrow
Rotate Right      Right Arrow
Thrust            Up Arrow
Fire              Space
Launch Ship       Enter


CHANGES
-------

0.0.2
-----

Changes to key handling code.
Make levels a little easier.


